<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> Gordon, Edmumd W., Beatrice L. Bridglall, and Aundra Saa Meroe. Preface. Supplemental Education: The Hidden Curriculum of High Academic Achievement. By Gordon, Edmumd W., Beatrice L. Bridglall, and Aundra Saa Meroe. Lanham, Maryland: Rowman &amp; Littlefield Publishers, Inc., 2005. ix-x.</li>
<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> Greene, Maxine. Introduction. The Hidden Curriculum and Moral Education. By Giroux, Henry and David Purpel. Berkeley, California: McCutchan Publishing Corporation, 1983. 1-5.</li>
