<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> Anyon, Jean. “Social Class and the Hidden Curriculum of Work.” The Hidden Curriculum and Moral Education. Ed. Giroux, Henry and David Purpel. Berkeley, California: McCutchan Publishing Corporation, 1983. 143-167.</li>
